HEADWORD: matrilineage
<hw>matrilineage</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The line of descent traced
through the maternal side of the family; the mother's line of
descent.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> enation, cognation.</syn>⟦br⟧
